    "body": "## Problem\r\nTerminal buffer scrollback is lost when a :terminal buffer is closed or Nvim restarts. (ref #28297)\r\nSolution. Still need to work implementing scrollback after buffer is loaded.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nAdd term_save() and term_load() functions in Lua for basic plain text terminal scrollback persistence using msgpack. This is an early proof-of-concept for my GSoC 2026 proposal. ANSI attribute support, marks integration, and session integration are planned but not yet implemented.\r\n",
